author: Kara
title: Kara
text: They were very easy to work with and provided prompt feedback. My only concern of 4/5 stars is that I feel it was a little bit pricy for the amount of pads I got. Otherwise they guided me very well and the product I received was exactly how I envisioned it to be. Thanks!
